Spent the last week on the beach and had so much fun rotating between a bunch of fun swimsuits.  This was a top favorite and just $32. What’s your favorite swimsuit style? 👙☀️🌊 GIVEAWAY: 🌊☀️👙Summer is right around the corner and you deserve to look & feel your best. Time to #treatyourself to a new swimsuit!!! I’ve teamed up with some of my favorite ladies to share our favorite Amazon suits for inspo 💗 We are giving THREE of you $100 PayPal cash to spoil yourself and buy yourself a new #swimsuit! 
